The available commands will be listed below:
Commands available for "fika" prefix:

Subcommand adminsettings:
fika adminsettings

Opens the settings GUI if you are a registered admin.

Subcommand fleaban:
fika fleaban
Bans a player from the flea for X days
Example: fika fleaban Nickname 7
Use 0 to ban indefinitely.

Subcommand forcelogout:
fika forcelogout
Forces a client to logout if they are in the menu
Example: fika forcelogout Nickname
Use all to logout everyone (including you).

Subcommand listprofiles:
fika listprofiles
Lists all profileIds and nicknames.
Nicknames are used for most commands

Subcommand removefleaban:
fika removefleaban
Unbans a player from the flea
Example: fika removefleaban Nickname

Subcommand sendmessage:
fika sendmessage
Sends a message to a client
Example: fika sendmessage Nickname hello
Use all as a nickname to send to everyone (including you).

Subcommand shutdownclient:
fika shutdownclient
Forces a headless client to shutdown
Example: fika shutdownclient Nickname

Subcommand spoofmessage:
fika spoofmessage
Spoofs a message to a client, using a fake account
Example: fika spoofmessage Nickname "Test" hello
Note: Fake account name has to be surrounded by quotes

The available commands will be listed below:
Commands available for "spt" prefix:

Subcommand trader:
spt trader 
 ======== 
 Sets the reputation or money spent to the input quantity through the message system.

	spt trader [trader] rep [quantity]
		Ex: spt trader prapor rep 2

	spt trader [trader] spend [quantity]
		Ex: spt trader therapist spend 1000000

Subcommand profile:
spt profile
========
Sets the profile level or skill to the desired level through the message system.

	spt profile level [desired level]
		Ex: spt profile level 20

	spt profile skill [skill name] [quantity]
		Ex: spt profile skill metabolism 51

Subcommand give:
spt give
========
Sends items to the player through the message system.

	spt give [template ID] [quantity]
		Ex: spt give 544fb25a4bdc2dfb738b4567 2

	spt give ["item name"] [quantity]
		Ex: spt give "pack of sugar" 10

	spt give [locale] ["item name"] [quantity]
		Ex: spt give fr "figurine de chat" 3

Subcommand give-gear-preset:
spt give-gear-preset
========
Sends items to the player through the message system.

	spt give-user-preset [equipmentBuilds.Id]

Subcommand give-user-stash-item:
spt give-user-stash-item
========
Sends items to the player through the message system.

	spt give-user-stash-item [stashItem.Id]

Subcommand give-user-preset:
